com.axeda.toolkit.ammp
Class Endpoint

java.lang.Object
  com.axeda.toolkit.ammp.Endpoint

public class Endpoint
extends Object

Class representing an AMMP Endpoint. An Endpoint can be constructed as follows: 

      // endpoint on default port (80)
      Endpoint endpoint = new Endpoint("http", "iotboston.com");
 
      // endpoint on port 52689, over HTTPS with read/write timeout of 3000ms
      Endpoint endpoint2 = new Endpoint("https", "myInstance.axeda.com", 52689).withTimeout(3000);
